{"about_the_game":"<strong>Astronium</strong> is a metroidvania with souls-like aspects, with a focus on combat and on getting weapons. Defeat strong enemies, survive ambushes, explore diferent biomes and meet interesting individuals on this hostile planet<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Just attacking is not enough.</h2><br>Mobs in Astronium can be very intelligent, don't expect them to watch you attack without making a move.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/extras/Combat.gif?t=1727829573\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Weapon Farm!</h2><br>Each enemy has a chance to drop a unique weapon, rare drops have special abilities! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/extras/Drop2.gif?t=1727829573\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Allies.. with a lot of charisma!</h2><br>Meet NPCs and sellers who will improve (or end) your life!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/extras/NPC.gif?t=1727829573\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Encounters and ambushes.</h2><br>Experience all kinds of situations in this hostile planet, offering goblin ambushes, snow monsters, marine creatures and a lot more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/extras/Astronium_0.77_ship_encounter_steam.gif?t=1727829573\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Boss battles.</h2><br>Each biome in astronium has his own ruler, sadly all of them rule with terror and fear.. But you will gladly put an end to their reigns in your journey to leave the planet!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/extras/Boss.gif?t=1727829573\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><br>\u25cf 4 Different biomes to explore.<br><br>\u25cf Over 40 Different weapons with unique movesets and powers!<br><br>\u25cf Quests, encounters and npcs all over the world!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Nature's Gift","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/b090e09150b34714b8dcfa08ed032f19e3ec3bdd.jpg"},{"name":"Bonfire Lit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/a3576e1301b1176eb9cdc3dfa05ebe582696277d.jpg"},{"name":"Mad Engineering","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/ffe1298ba5205ea67be69abd48f0299ea56c26ad.jpg"},{"name":"The Summoner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/fd05c4951c830f270ad00133980582863b59e146.jpg"},{"name":"Goblin Zone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/1e7de839a0509579bf91f5459fcfac1f67fb2eac.jpg"},{"name":"Swordsmanship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/657968fd521bed992a487dabeaa713e42473ff11.jpg"},{"name":"Pest Control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/aa0d747e8cefa6456d134c7831e6bc617a85c7d7.jpg"},{"name":" Immortality In A Nutshell","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/a339464badc6d858999f5c67af6dd492812c0acc.jpg"},{"name":"The Goblin King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/5e706433cedb293506e3145daa89e11902b1fbe5.jpg"},{"name":"Scarce Technology","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1677380/69a4cff2b9c4c055ca8938155c9da5c2ec563678.jpg"}],"total":25},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727829573","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727829573","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677380/